?  Game info:                                                                  ?
?                                                                              ?
?  Imagine having a Kung Fu Fight with string puppets, except you don't have   ?
?  to worry about getting the strings tangled up, and you don't                ?
?  have to have a kung fu fight.                                               ?
?  You control the characters on screen with the mouse there are no            ?
?  pre-scripted animations in the game.                                        ?
?                                                                              ?
?  It's all up to you! To walk, you have to literally pick up one foot,        ?
?  then place it in front of the other.                                        ?
?  Sounds tricky maybe, but it doesn't take long before you're spinning        ?
?  through the air like a Russian gymnast.                                     ?
?                                                                              ?
?  This means you get to create your own style, and can act out whatever       ?
?  you feel like, and of course, if you really feel like it, you               ?
?  can have a fight.                                                           ?
?                                                                              ?
?  It's about Chi power.                                                       ?
?                                                                              ?
?  More game information can be found on:                                      ?
?  www.ragdollkungfu.com - www.steampowered.com                                ?
